OL,3,CThief jailed for targeting elderly
OL,4,Cpeople in distraction burglaries
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for burgling
OL,7,Fhomes in Wickham and Gosport.
OL,9,FOn 28 January 2023, a woman in her 80s
OL,10,Freceived a knock at her door in
OL,11,FBuddens Road, Wickham, where she was
OL,12,Ffaced with 21-year-old Larky Hughes
OL,13,Fwho told her he was there to do
OL,14,Fgardening work for her.
OL,16,FShe allowed him into her house, where
OL,17,Fhe stole #80 from her handbag before
OL,18,Fleaving without completing any work.
