OL,6,FThe legitimate gardener employed by
OL,7,Fthe victim was spoken to and confirmed
OL,8,Fhe had not sent anyone to the address
OL,9,Fto complete work on his behalf.
OL,11,FIn a separate incident on 13 November
OL,12,F2023, Hughes targeted another woman,
OL,13,Fthis time in Highfield Road in Gosport.
OL,15,FThe woman, aged in her 70s, received a
OL,16,Fknock at the door from Hughes, who
OL,17,Fagain offered to do gardening work.
OL,19,FHughes was invited through the house
OL,20,Finto the garden to discuss, but the
OL,21,Fwoman soon declined the offer of work.
