OL,6,FHughes, of The Spur in Wickham,
OL,7,Fappeared at Portsmouth Crown Court
OL,8,Fwhere he was jailed for four and a
OL,9,Fhalf years.
OL,11,FDC Zoe Barker said: "Distraction
OL,12,Fburglaries and other forms of doorstep
OL,13,Fcrime often see some of our most
OL,14,Fvulnerable members of the community
OL,15,Ftargeted and manipulated into thinking
OL,16,Fthey can trust the person knocking on
OL,17,Ftheir door.
