OL,6,F"It is a disgraceful act to prey on a
OL,7,Fvulnerable person in this way for
OL,8,Ffinancial gain, and we take robust
OL,9,Faction against anyone who is
OL,10,Fidentified as being involved in this
OL,11,Ftype of crime.
OL,13,F"We want people to be alert to these
OL,14,Ftypes of criminals, and encourage you
OL,15,Fto share our crime prevention advice
OL,16,Fwith any elderly neighbours and
OL,17,Frelatives to ensure they are aware of
OL,18,Fhow they can stay protected."
